snippet.textDisplay:
Sir, awesome work. The track is very well designed. 

Vithhal teedee took my heart. 

but this KHALASI MAN. What a vibe, WHAT A VIBE. 

I have a feeling that this is going to be the massive obsession around the world, the track has hiphop vibe, reggae, and the chorus is beautifully designed that doesn’t feel like a chorus.

Mare aa geet badha ne sambhdaavu chhe.

Sauthi saro part e chhe k, aa mari j matru bhasha ma chhe, ane mare ene samjavani koshish nathi karvi padi. 

Bija coke studio na geeto ma mare always lyrics jova pade chhe. 

Vithhal teedi 
Mara nand ji laaal 
And now this KHALASI 

YOU ARE AMAZING ADITYA GHADVI.
